"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Tums&reg; Ultra: 1000 mg [contains tartrazine; peppermint flavor; equivalent to elemental calcium 400 mg]",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Tums&reg; Ultra: 1000 mg [contains tartrazine; spearmint flavor; equivalent to elemental calcium 400 mg]",
