"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:2em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Tablet, softchew, oral:",
"    </p>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:-2em;margin-left:4em;text-align:justify;\">",
"     Rolaids&reg; Extra Strength: 1177 mg [contains coconut oil, soya lecithin; vanilla cr&egrave;me flavor; equivalent to elemental calcium 471 mg]",
